{"title":"小骑手","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小骑手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位小朋友，是个小骑手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥一挥马鞭，挽一挽衣袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要往哪儿走？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你这神气，谁也能猜透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想跨上骏马，把本领练就，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学骑趁年幼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马背当摇篮，草原度春秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨十年久；待到赛马会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你显身手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐　匡　木刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉　诗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}